params._recipient: Recipient of the NFT. Must be ERC721 compatible if a contract
params._sfrxEthAmount: Amount of sfrxETH to redeem (in shares / balanceOf)

returns.earlyExitFee: Early NFT back to frxETH exit fee given as a percentage with 1e6 precision
returns.queueLengthSecs: Current wait time (in seconds) a new redeemer would have. Should be close to Beacon.
returns.redemptionFee: Redemption fee given as a percentage with 1e6 precision
